}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 130-132.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   Benvenuto (comm. to these verses) understands the simile as having the \softline
following meaning: 'Just as that most renowned island, Delos, once sent forth the two most \softline
